boj]]\n| align=\"right\" | 2\n| align=\"right\" | \n| align=\"right\" | 0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\"| [[Gacko]]\n| align=\"right\" | 10\n| align=\"right\" | \n| align=\"right\" | 0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\" | [[Gradi\u0161ka, Bosnia and Herzegovina|Gradi\u0161ka]]\n| align=\"right\" | 15\n| align=\"right\" | \n| align=\"right\" | 0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\" | [[Isto\u010dna Ilid\u017ea]]\n| align=\"right\" | 6\n| align=\"right\" | \n| align=\"right\" | 0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\" | [[Isto\u010dno Novo Sarajevo]]\n| align=\"right\" | 1\n| align=\"right\" | \n| align=\"right\" | 0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\" | [[Kalinovik]]\n| align=\"right\" | 1\n| align=\"right\" | \n| align=\"right\" | 0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\" |[[Kne\u017eevo, Bosnia and Herzegovina|Kne\u017eevo]]\n| align=\"right\" | 16\n| align=\"right\" | \n| align=\"right\" | 3\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\"| [[Kotor Varo\u0161]]\n| align=\"right\"| 24\n| align=\"right\"| \n| align=\"right\"| 0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\"| [[Kozarska Dubica]]\n| align=\"right\"| 11\n| align=\"right\"| \n| align=\"right\"| 7\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\"| [[Lakta\u0161i]]\n| align=\"right\" | 42\n| align=\"right\" | \n| align=\"right\" | 9\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\"|[[Mili\u0107i, Republika Srpska|Mili\u0107i]]\n| align=\"right\" | 1\n| align=\"right\" | \n| align=\"right\" | 0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\"| [[Modri\u010da]]\n| align=\"right\" | 6\n| align=\"right\" | \n| align=\"right\" | 2\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\"| [[Mrkonji\u0107 Grad]]\n| align=\"right\" | 12\n| align=\"right\" | \n| align=\"right\" | 1\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\"| [[Nevesinje]]\n| align=\"right\" | 14\n| align=\"right\" | \n| align=\"right\" | 0\n|-\n| al